'Times New Roman'; font-size:10pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:10pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_ftn16"></a><a href="#_ftnref16">[16]</a><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:10pt"> These recommendations were first made within 22 recommendations to improve defences against corruption in local government set out by TI-UK in the ‘Corruption in UK Local Government’ report - </span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:Georgia; font-size:8pt">h</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:Georgia; font-size:8pt">ttp://www.transparency.org.uk/our-work/publications/10-publications/747-corruption-in-uk-local-government-the-mounting-risks</span></p></body></html>